# Program keypairs go here. Generated locally; not committed.
#
# Phase A bootstrap (run from this directory's parent, settle-protocol/):
#
#   solana-keygen new -o programs-ika/keys/dwallet_router-keypair.json --no-bip39-passphrase
#   anchor keys sync   # picks up the new pubkey and patches declare_id! in lib.rs
#
# After deploy, the deployed program id should match the keypair pubkey:
#
#   solana address -k programs-ika/keys/dwallet_router-keypair.json
